      "message": "Is the idea here that _canvas\u0027s matrix is always kept as identity?\n\nIt\u0027s a little funny to see a field _currentTransform held in parallel to _canvas... it might be more natural to actually allow _canvas\u0027 matrix to track the current transform?  That\u0027d make it so those places below where you manually multiply the current transform with other matrices a lot simpler.  Calls to translate just map to translate calls on the canvas, etc.",
